{
  "info": {
    "name": "Fusio Fantasy API - Clean Collection",
    "description": "Clean and organized API collection for Fusio Fantasy portfolio competition game.\n\nThis collection provides a comprehensive set of endpoints for:\n- Wallet-based authentication\n- Portfolio creation and management\n- Game participation and tracking\n- Asset management and price tracking\n- Transaction processing\n- Admin management\n- User notifications\n\n## Authentication Flow\n1. Get nonce for wallet address\n2. Sign message with wallet\n3. Verify signature to get JWT token\n4. Use JWT token for authenticated requests\n\n## Environment Variables\n- baseUrl: API base URL (default: http://localhost:5000)\n- jwt_token: JWT token from authentication\n- wallet_address: User's wallet address\n\n## Game Types\n- DEFI: DeFi assets and protocols\n- TRADFI: Traditional finance assets\n\n## Portfolio Status\n- PENDING: Awaiting transaction confirmation\n- ACTIVE: Currently in game\n- COMPLETED: Game finished\n- FAILED: Transaction failed or cancelled",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "version": "1.0.0"
  },
